OL,5, A man has pleaded guilty to stalking by
OL,6, sending intimidating comments to former
OL,7, BBC Breakfast presenter Louise Minchin 
OL,8, and her adult daughter on Instagram.   
OL,10,FCarl Davies, 44, was due to stand trial
OL,11,Fbut changed his plea to both charges to
OL,12,Fguilty.                                
OL,14,FDavies, of Flint, Flintshire, admitted 
OL,15,Fcausing alarm or distress to both      
OL,16,FLouise and Mia Minchin in July 2020.   
OL,18,FAn order was made for him at Caernarfon
OL,19,FCrown Court not to refer to the women  
OL,20,Fon any social media site.              
